    "title": "イクノ式万全メソッド",
    "text": [
        {
            "jpName": "",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "1人、コースを見て回っている\r\nイクノディクタスを見かけた。",
            "enText": "I saw one man, Ichnodictus, \nlooking around the course.",
            "nextBlock": 2,
            "origClipLength": 84,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 95,
                    "pathId": -63443822887956883
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 95,
                    "pathId": -6151208619619831976
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -4452448514695486337,
            "blockIdx": 1
        },
        {
            "jpName": "イクノディクタス",
            "enName": "Ikuno Dictus",
            "jpText": "あの位置にゲートを設置するとして、\r\n観客席からの距離を考えると……ふむ。",
            "enText": "If you put the gate in that position, given \nthe distance from the spectator area… hmm.",
            "nextBlock": 3,
            "origClipLength": 93,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "何してるの？",
                    "enText": "What are you doing?",
                    "nextBlock": 3
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 66,
                    "pathId": -7923466832406186277
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 104,
                    "pathId": -6105214555443731740
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -9191522463560153779,
            "blockIdx": 2
        },
        {
            "jpName": "イクノディクタス",
            "enName": "Ikuno Dictus",
            "jpText": "今度行われるオリエンテーションでの\r\n模擬レースの準備を任されましたので、\nそちらの下見をしています。",
            "enText": "I've been asked to prepare a mock race for \nthe upcoming orientation, so I'm doing some \npreliminary work on that.",
            "nextBlock": 4,
            "origClipLength": 111,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 87,
                    "pathId": 4026775187232979841
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 122,
                    "pathId": -4964423784023895534
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 684027342622275967,
            "blockIdx": 3
        },
        {
            "jpName": "イクノディクタス",
            "enName": "Ikuno Dictus",
            "jpText": "……と、すみませんが、\r\nそこをどいていただけますか。\nコースの幅を測りたいので。",
            "enText": "… and excuse me, can you move out \nof the way? We want to measure \nthe width of the course.",
            "nextBlock": 5,
            "origClipLength": 98,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "随分と念入りだね",
                    "enText": "You're very meticulous.",
                    "nextBlock": 5
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 81,
                    "pathId": 2139520776970726277
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 109,
                    "pathId": 6050782000734664429
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -1304212988423131520,
            "blockIdx": 4
        },
        {
            "jpName": "イクノディクタス",
            "enName": "Ikuno Dictus",
            "jpText": "そうした面を評価いただき、\r\nこの件を任せていただいたのです。",
            "enText": "It was this aspect of our work that led us \nto take on this project.",
            "nextBlock": 6,
            "origClipLength": 85,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 54,
                    "pathId": -5363144472228224864
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 96,
                    "pathId": -7927467439557768327
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 5179201406739017847,
            "blockIdx": 5
        },
        {
            "jpName": "イクノディクタス",
            "enName": "Ikuno Dictus",
            "jpText": "手を抜いて大事になっては、\r\nオリエンテーションどころではありません。",
            "enText": "If you cut corners and get into trouble, you \nwill not be able to attend the orientation.",
            "nextBlock": 7,
            "origClipLength": 90,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 62,
                    "pathId": 9041942829528938093
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 101,
                    "pathId": 9019991313397505230
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -7914437101095543872,
            "blockIdx": 6
        },
        {
            "jpName": "イクノディクタス",
            "enName": "Ikuno Dictus",
            "jpText": "では、まだやるべきことが\r\n残っていますので、これにて……。",
            "enText": "There is still work to be done, \nso I will leave you…",
            "nextBlock": 8,
            "origClipLength": 84,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "全部1人でやるの？",
                    "enText": "Do you do everything by yourself?",
                    "nextBlock": 8
                },
                {
                    "jpText": "随分と熱心なんだね",
                    "enText": "You're very enthusiastic.",
                    "nextBlock": 18
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 47,
                    "pathId": 3062752797132745495
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 95,
                    "pathId": -4916953551471812212
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -207302396622386505,
            "blockIdx": 7
        },
        {
            "jpName": "イクノディクタス",
            "enName": "Ikuno Dictus",
            "jpText": "ええ。任されたのは私1人だけですが、\r\n要領を得て動けば問題ありません。",
            "enText": "Yes. I'm the only one in charge, but as long \nas I'm on point, I'm good to go.",
            "nextBlock": 9,
            "origClipLength": 91,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 60,
                    "pathId": 6751352223689169550
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 102,
                    "pathId": -9059712080707994080
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -1838128148046060056,
            "blockIdx": 8
        },
        {
            "jpName": "",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "いくら要領がいいとはいえ、\r\n1人では大変なはずだと思い、\n声をかけようとしたのだが……。",
            "enText": "I tried to reach out to her, but I knew that \neven though she was good at what she did, it \nwould be hard for her to do it alone…",
            "nextBlock": 10,
            "origClipLength": 103,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 114,
                    "pathId": -4870649290751057519
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 114,
                    "pathId": -1714714009729303949
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 8836358436996481213,
            "blockIdx": 9
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ウマ娘A",
            "enName": "Horsegirl A",
            "jpText": "あー！　イクノさんが\r\nまた1人でなんかやろうとしてるー！",
            "enText": "Aaah! Ikuno-san is trying to do \nsomething by herself again!",
            "nextBlock": 11,
            "origClipLength": 82,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 142,
                    "pathId": 2610561678405928402
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 93,
                    "pathId": 4895894572717928180
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 93,
                    "pathId": 5920443646451005286
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -7124673347518964661,
            "blockIdx": 10
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ウマ娘B",
            "enName": "Horsegirl B",
            "jpText": "大変な事を任された時は頼ってくださいって\r\n言ったじゃないですか。",
            "enText": "You told me that I could rely on you when I \nwas asked to do something difficult.",
            "nextBlock": 12,
            "origClipLength": 88,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 132,
                    "pathId": 8312028071394378447
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 99,
                    "pathId": 4764252249123106152
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 99,
                    "pathId": 2901296621040707197
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 8293459016990811574,
            "blockIdx": 11
        },
        {
            "jpName": "イクノディクタス",
            "enName": "Ikuno Dictus",
            "jpText": "しかし、任されたのは私で――",
            "enText": "But it was I who was left in charge—",
            "nextBlock": 13,
            "origClipLength": 63,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 45,
                    "pathId": 3937117960975281607
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 21,
                    "pathId": 2347535212098475802
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 74,
                    "pathId": -1158122447641729425
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -470834613926683642,
            "blockIdx": 12
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ウマ娘A",
            "enName": "Horsegirl A",
            "jpText": "まあまあ、1人でやるより\r\nみんなでやった方が、\n早く終わるじゃないですかー！",
            "enText": "Well, well, well, it goes faster when you do \nit together than when you do it alone!",
            "nextBlock": 14,
            "origClipLength": 95,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 106,
                    "pathId": 1470448489059884373
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 106,
                    "pathId": -971492355427380009
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -2574299714075073170,
            "blockIdx": 13
        },
        {
            "jpName": "イクノディクタス",
            "enName": "Ikuno Dictus",
            "jpText": "……わかりました。\r\nそれでは、2人はそれぞれ旗を持って――",
            "enText": "… I understand. Now, you two \nwill each take a flag and—",
            "nextBlock": 15,
            "origClipLength": 84,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 67,
                    "pathId": -5684102408200647571
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 95,
                    "pathId": -8004576786325560445
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 3870757783746958620,
            "blockIdx": 14
        },
        {
            "jpName": "イクノディクタス",
            "enName": "Ikuno Dictus",
            "jpText": "あ……すみません。指示を出さなければ\r\nなりませんので、これで失礼します。",
            "enText": "I'm sorry… I have to give instructions, \nso I'll leave you now.",
            "nextBlock": 16,
            "origClipLength": 93,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 62,
                    "pathId": 3880610099009059093
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 104,
                    "pathId": -6830615309806832719
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -3544912938975018530,
            "blockIdx": 15
        },
        {
            "jpName": "イクノディクタス",
            "enName": "Ikuno Dictus",
            "jpText": "観客席からの見え方を把握しておきたいので、\r\n手前と奥のコーナーに立って、\nそれぞれ旗を振ってください。その後は――",
            "enText": "Please stand in the front and back \ncorners and wave a flag each, so that \nwe know how you will be seen from \nthe audience. After that—",
            "nextBlock": 17,
            "origClipLength": 120,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 102,
                    "pathId": 4529763143612134773
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 102,
                    "pathId": 6700648506391814291
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 508743399696399499,
            "blockIdx": 16
        },
        {
            "jpName": "",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "彼女はとても友人に慕われているようだ。\r\nこれなら、こちらからの助けは\n必要なさそうである。",
            "enText": "She seems to be very much loved \nby her friends. She doesn't seem \nto need any help from us.",
            "nextBlock": -1,
            "origClipLength": 105,
            "pathId": -8252356416227603556,
            "blockIdx": 17
        },
        {
            "jpName": "イクノディクタス",
            "enName": "Ikuno Dictus",
            "jpText": "ええ。当然です。\r\n熱がこもらないはずがありません。",
            "enText": "Yes, of course. Of course. It's impossible \nfor heat not to build up.",
            "nextBlock": 19,
            "origClipLength": 78,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 94,
                    "pathId": 7488006601791956264
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 61,
                    "pathId": -5109592969045153753
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 89,
                    "pathId": 5671682854526809800
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -2057402681979386546,
            "blockIdx": 18
        },
        {
            "jpName": "イクノディクタス",
            "enName": "Ikuno Dictus",
            "jpText": "オリエンテーションは、\r\n外部の方がお見えになられます。",
            "enText": "The orientation is open to \nall external visitors.",
            "nextBlock": 20,
            "origClipLength": 81,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 34,
                    "pathId": -3876970188643285268
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 50,
                    "pathId": -2884022282850220230
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 92,
                    "pathId": 458713543337693690
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -6313817776347451741,
            "blockIdx": 19
        },
        {
            "jpName": "イクノディクタス",
            "enName": "Ikuno Dictus",
            "jpText": "中にはいずれこの学園に来る\r\nウマ娘もいるかもしれません……。",
            "enText": "Some of the girls may eventually \ncome to the school…",
            "nextBlock": 21,
            "origClipLength": 85,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 96,
                    "pathId": -8365849691422957974
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 70,
                    "pathId": 3829170262318560752
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 96,
                    "pathId": -693509584830704319
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 6222580544595391786,
            "blockIdx": 20
        },
        {
            "jpName": "イクノディクタス",
            "enName": "Ikuno Dictus",
            "jpText": "私はそんな子たちに、安全に\r\n心ゆくまで楽しんでもらいたいのです。",
            "enText": "I want them to be safe and have \nfun to their heart's content.",
            "nextBlock": 22,
            "origClipLength": 88,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 35,
                    "pathId": 9204142001881917769
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 60,
                    "pathId": -809535814685678386
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 99,
                    "pathId": -3816002389859725341
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 2989852599961657222,
            "blockIdx": 21
        },
        {
            "jpName": "イクノディクタス",
            "enName": "Ikuno Dictus",
            "jpText": "もっとも、理由はそれだけではありません。",
            "enText": "But that's not the only reason.",
            "nextBlock": 23,
            "origClipLength": 71,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 51,
                    "pathId": 8319496970448178446
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 82,
                    "pathId": 4099663283572039731
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 8866316843739410434,
            "blockIdx": 22
        },
        {
            "jpName": "イクノディクタス",
            "enName": "Ikuno Dictus",
            "jpText": "地域を盛り上げる催し物という観点からも、\r\nこのオリエンテーションは老若男女問わず\n楽しめる設計である必要がありまして――",
            "enText": "From the point of view of a community event, \nthe orientation had to be designed to be fun \nfor young and old alike.",
            "nextBlock": 24,
            "origClipLength": 124,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 140,
                    "pathId": -9045624108442436338
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 177,
                    "pathId": 7206616045510956209
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 135,
                    "pathId": 5639058448334390344
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -5044475051894438955,
            "blockIdx": 23
        },
        {
            "jpName": "",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "イクノディクタスのオリエンテーションへの\r\n熱意と、いかに楽しんでもらうか\nという設計を知る事が出来た……。",
            "enText": "The enthusiasm of Ichnodictus for the \norientation and how it was designed to be \nfun was very evident…",
            "nextBlock": -1,
            "origClipLength": 115,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 148,
                    "pathId": -2028320753995087278
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 126,
                    "pathId": 3487735696302503131
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 126,
                    "pathId": 7317220490056083298
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 7204392503913823742,
            "blockIdx": 24
        }
    ],
